Pathway explored : REACTOME ADENYLATE CYCLASE INHIBITORY PATHWAY

This pathway contain 14 genes.

In these 14 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes in the enrichment.

Adcy5, Adcy6, Adcy9
